53/** Get the number of integers in this table. This is NOT the
54 * same thing as the number of elements.
55 * @param tbl the table
56 * @return the number of integers in the table
57 */
58yyskel_static flex_int32_t yytbl_calc_total_len (const struct yytbl_data *tbl)
59{
60 flex_uint32_t n;
61
62 /* total number of ints */
63 n = tbl->td_lolen;
64 if (tbl->td_hilen > 0)
65 n *= tbl->td_hilen;
66
67 if (tbl->td_id == YYTD_ID_TRANSITION)
68 n *= 2;
69 return (flex_int32_t) n;
70}
